## GitHub App Integration

```yaml
# Coolify GitHub App Configuration
coolify:
  integration:
    type: 'github-app'
    name: '@Coolify'
    scope: 'private'
    features:
      - Auto-deployment on push
      - Branch protection rules
      - Deployment status updates
      - PR environment previews
      - Automatic cleanup

  # Deployment triggers
  triggers:
    push:
      branches: [main, develop]
    pull_request:
      types: [opened, synchronize]

  # Environment configuration
  environments:
    production:
      branch: main
      auto_deploy: false
      requires_approval: true
    staging:
      branch: develop
      auto_deploy: true
      requires_approval: false
```
